node.text: If you like Dry Creek Sonoma wine, this is your jam. (It’s not jammy though)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wine in Palos Verdes Peninsula with @crystalhoang, @kellyaxelrad, @bookervineyard, @baxel1, @wine1percent, @azimut_yachts, and @gravitymalibu. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: What I learned about wine today… @bookervineyard makes a good Grenache and that’s a great pair…ing with the charcuterie board. @gravitymalibu #yachtlife #grenache #pasorobleswinecountry #azimutyachts #redwine #🍷#🛥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wine in Seared with @baxel1, @searedpetaluma, and @titus_vineyards.

node.text: Checking out Petaluma and found this great steakhouse @searedpetaluma and paired a tight meal with @titus_vineyards 2016 #cabernetsauvignon. #napavalleywine #petalumacalifornia #sonomacounty #eeeeeats #foodie #wine #redwine #🍷

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wine in Manhattan Beach, California with @kellyaxelrad, @melanieperret, @baxel1, @garyfarrellwinery, and @slayitaliankitchen. May be an image of food.

node.text: Finally made it to @slayitaliankitchen and brought a cellar selection Russian River Pinot Noir by @garyfarrellwinery. I can’t recommend the #OssoBuco enough. It melted off the bone and paired delightfully with or wine selections bright cherry, tobacco and library leather and a tart finish. #wine #pinotnoir #ossobuco #manhattanbeach #eeeeeats #redwine #🍷

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wine in Manhattan Beach, California with @mrclassicjones, @mallieclairee, @kellyaxelrad, @melanieperret, @baxel1, @sawyer_coye, @champagneshotgun, and @carnivalwinecompany. May be an image of 1 person, crustacean and indoor.

node.text: That’s about as #louisiana as you can get in #cali. Brought out our very own @carnivalwinecompany #blancdeblancs for a very fun occasion🎂 #sparklingwine #crawfishboil #sonomawine #🍾#🥂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wine in Manhattan Beach, California with @mallieclairee, @sawyer_coye, @bonnemaman_us, @lindt, and @carnivalwinecompany. May be an image of fruit.

node.text: Looks like @mallieclairee has a good Sunday plan. #charcuterieboard @carnivalwinecompany #rosé #beachdays #wine #🥂#🍾

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wine in Santa Rosa, California with @foreignservice, @kellyaxelrad, @baxel1, @socomeatco, @the_real_boasy, @jayalexis2, @madoromvineyards, @champagneshotgun, and @steak. May be an image of food and indoor.
Photo by Wine in Titus Vineyards with @foreignservice, @kellyaxelrad, @baxel1, @titus_vineyards, and @jayalexis2. May be an image of nature.

node.text: Out and about on another sunny day in #NorCal #winecountry with @kellyaxelrad and a little #cabernetfranc @titus_vineyards. #napavalley #redwine
